  "route_consequence": "The trace-normalized recursion G_j = X_j^*X_j/||X_j||_2^2 + eta G_{j-1} is an online, scale-free packet statistic. With eta=1/512, its clock-rank packet has a 192-bit terminal relative residual below 1.2e-5 at all five anchors and improves the raw unweighted prefix packet by at least three orders of magnitude. Every Davis-Kahan perturbation/gap ratio exceeds one million, so principal-angle continuity is quantitatively unavailable even though captured energy is stable. The next proof should control weighted Rayleigh leakage directly, not singular-vector angles.",
